The EOE team encountered some issues, they need our support:

# P1 Issue – Website – Deliveries to named houses are not available; _Prioritized as core web functionality & will disrupt a significant portion of potential users. -_ {color:#ff991f}_Waiting for discussion and confirmations from Dana and PO_{color}
# P2 Issue – Mobile Apps – Payment Gateway Error; _While effectively making the app untenable we are hopeful that the deployment on Sunday will resolve this & ensure that we can trade on the app._ *_Dima_* _-_ {color:#ff991f}_Waiting for updates_{color}
# P2 Issue – Gophr Integration – Deliveries containing Age Related products that couriers need to Age verify are not showing on the couriers platform through the flag in the Jobs; _Legal requirement needs resolving please can you raise with_ *_Long_* _if needed -_ {color:#36b37e}_DONE and wait for deployment_{color}
# P3 Issue – Mobile Apps – Deliveries to named houses are impacted from a customer flow with additional & confusing steps; _Users can push through this on the app we can take this into 2024 if not resolvable in line with P1 Website issue -_ {color:#ff991f}_Waiting for discussion and confirmations from Dana and PO_{color}

The number of order is not correct in order count. 

